                    '18437', 'Spandine', '', 'Spandine is the father of Spandam and was CP9''s chief 22 years ago. He led the "investigation" in Ohara and was responsible for summoning the Buster Call. First Appearance: Chapter 392; Episode 275 (source: onepiece.wikia.com)', 
