                ) VALUES (
                    '19375', 'Macro', '', 'Macro is a Fishman pirate and the leader the Macro Fishman Pirates. He first appeared in Hatchan''s Sea-Floor Stroll mini-series. Macro is a Fishman whose fish half is a fish called Macropharynx, a Japanese scientific name for Gulper Eels. His fish half is specifically the Gulper Eel classified as Pelican Eel.', 
