                    '21381', 'Mani', '', 'Mani (マニ) is a member of the Bellamy Pirates. She is a female fighter, and is the curly-haired black-skinned beauty who was first seen side-by-side with Rivers. When Nami refused Bellamy''s offer to buy her off the Straw Hat Pirates, she and Lilly gave each other a suprised glance at her response. Despite being a "fighter", she, like the rest of the crew did nothing to stop Luffy. First Appearance: Chapter 223; Episode 146 Source: http://onepiece.wikia.com/wiki/Mani', 
