                ) VALUES (
                    '21535', 'Cricket Montblanc', '', 'Montblanc Cricket is an inhabitant of Jaya Island, living in a small home behind the facade of a castle. He is the distant descendant of Montblanc Norland. He and the Saruyama Alliance aided the Straw hats in getting to Skypiea. (Source: One Piece Wiki)', 
