                    '21556', 'Zala', '', 'Miss Doublefinger (Miss New Years Eve in the 4Kids dub), real name Paula, is the second highest ranking female officer agent in Baroque Works. First Appearance: Chapter 160; Episode 103 Devil Fruit: Toge Toge no Mi (Thorn Thorn Fruit)', 
