                    '21806', 'Kokoro', '', 'Kokoro (ココロ) is the main conductor of the Sea Train, Puffing Tom, at the station just outside of Water 7. She has a granddaughter named Chimney, who accompanies her everywhere. (Source: One Piece Wiki)', 
