                    '22802', 'Shura', '', 'Skyrider Shura (スカイライダー・シュラ, Sukairaidā Shura), the second priest of the Upper Yard, punishes criminals with the Ordeal of String. He tangles his enemies in nearly-invisible and unbreakable string and then attacks with his lance named Burn Lance. that has a Heat Dial inside. He rides a flying monster bird named Fuza, who has a Fire Dial in its mouth that allows it to breathe fire. First Appearance: 	 Chapter 241; Episode 155 Source: http://onepiece.wikia.com/wiki/Shura', 
