                ) VALUES (
                    '23024', 'Laki', '', 'Laki is one of the Shandian warriors that fought to take back Upper Yard from Eneru. She is good friends with Kamakiri and Aisa. She used a gun as a weapon and lost to Eneru in the Survival Game as she tried to warn Wiper that he couldn''t kill Eneru, but she later recovers as the war ends. The last time she is seen she is taking a walk on the Vearth with Norla, Conis and Aisa. (Source: One Piece Wiki)', 
