                ) VALUES (
                    '23535', 'Erik', '', 'Erik is a member of the Rebel Army in Arabasta led by Kohza. He has a little beard and wears a dark hat. He''s from Suiren, a town that has been completely dried out. His friend is Farafra. First Appearance: Chapter 167; Episode 105 (Source: One Piece Wikia)', 
