                ) VALUES (
                    '28509', 'Klabautermann', '', 'A Klabautermann is said to be a water spirit (or fairy) that dwells on ships that are well cared for and is basically an incarnation of the ship. It is a merry and diligent creature that is said to warn sailors when a ship''s in danger and help in bigger ways sometimes. They are normally considered to be only a legend among seafarers. (Source: One Piece Wikia)', 
